*Došao* je u njenu sobu i zagrlio je (He came into her room and hugged her).

On je *došao* kući pre nego što je znao šta će biti sa njim (He came home before he knew what would be with him).

Njegov sin je *došao* kući pre podne (His son came home before noon).

Učiteljica je *došla* u sobu da proveri da li su učenici učili (The teacher came into the room to check if the students had studied).

*Došli* su u restoran da bi popili piće (They came to the restaurant to have a drink).